<img src="http://c.biz-file.com/c/1804/436858.jpg?2" alt="#OneShow2018: UX/UI finalists revealed!" width="625" height="325">This year’s ‘UX/UI categories include; 'web – utility’, web – user experience’, ‘mobile – utility’, ‘mobile – user experience’, ‘digital – cross-channel, ‘digital/physical cross-channel’, ‘craft – interface design’, ‘craft – dynamic data visualization’, and ‘innovation in UX/UI – single channel’.Click here for the full list of finalists, which includes all the gold, silver and bronze pencils as well as merit winners. The winners and full award details will be announced during One Show Creative Week in New York, from 7 to 11 May.You can view these and other One Show entries by browsing this year’s finalist showcase. Visit our One Show special section for all the latest updates!